1
00:01:13,039 --> 00:01:14,000
Hello, cousin.

2
00:01:14,440 --> 00:01:15,970
I want to borrow some money.

3
00:01:16,280 --> 00:01:17,360
Just 3,000.

4
00:01:17,800 --> 00:01:18,640
Can you lend me?

5
00:01:18,640 --> 00:01:20,240
What are you dreaming about?

6
00:01:20,320 --> 00:01:21,720
I'm not an ATM.

7
00:01:21,920 --> 00:01:23,320
Besides, you're an adult now.

8
00:01:23,320 --> 00:01:25,160
You have to learn to be independent.

9
00:01:25,160 --> 00:01:26,680
Okay, I see.

10
00:01:28,440 --> 00:01:29,240
Wait a minute.

11
00:01:30,880 --> 00:01:31,560
What's wrong?

12
00:01:31,560 --> 00:01:33,620
I actually have a big job for you here.

13
00:01:34,440 --> 00:01:35,600
Okay, no problem.

14
00:01:39,800 --> 00:01:40,640
Dahuo.

15
00:01:42,880 --> 00:01:44,240
Dahuo, Dahuo,

16
00:01:44,320 --> 00:01:46,400
you're so cute.

17
00:01:48,280 --> 00:01:49,120
Listen to me.

18
00:01:49,160 --> 00:01:51,280
You must behave these days.

19
00:01:51,479 --> 00:01:52,640
Once I pay off the debt,

20
00:01:52,640 --> 00:01:54,720
I promise you'll live a good life.

21
00:01:54,800 --> 00:01:56,800
Just follow me from now on.

22
00:02:03,880 --> 00:02:04,480
Hello?

23
00:02:05,160 --> 00:02:06,480
Hello, it's me,

24
00:02:07,160 --> 00:02:07,760
Su Wan.

25
00:02:08,240 --> 00:02:10,440
The one from the police station last night.

26
00:02:10,440 --> 00:02:11,800
Add me on WeChat,

27
00:02:11,880 --> 00:02:13,120
and send me an address.

28
00:02:13,120 --> 00:02:14,180
I'll come find you.

29
00:02:14,280 --> 00:02:15,400
Make sure you send it to me.

30
00:02:15,400 --> 00:02:15,840
Hello?

31
00:02:18,760 --> 00:02:20,960
You just do whatever comes to your mind.

32
00:02:22,079 --> 00:02:25,140
Aren't you the one who does whatever comes to your mind?

33
00:02:30,160 --> 00:02:32,200
You love being a people pleaser so much.

34
00:02:32,200 --> 00:02:33,640
If the factory goes bankrupt,

35
00:02:33,640 --> 00:02:34,600
can you face Dad?

36
00:02:34,760 --> 00:02:36,360
I'll figure out a way to get the money.

37
00:02:36,360 --> 00:02:38,960
I'll pay it back to the factory in a couple of days.

38
00:02:38,960 --> 00:02:40,000
Keke, come here.

39
00:02:41,160 --> 00:02:42,240
It might bite someone if it comes in.

40
00:02:42,240 --> 00:02:42,880
I'm sorry.

41
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:44,760
Well, I'm looking for someone.

42
00:02:47,840 --> 00:02:49,240
You have a female friend.

43
00:02:49,880 --> 00:02:50,680
Wait a minute.

44
00:02:50,680 --> 00:02:53,079
Did you give those thousands of yuan to her?

45
00:02:56,880 --> 00:02:59,760
So, did you come here today to fix the car,

46
00:02:59,880 --> 00:03:00,760
or fix him?

47
00:03:01,360 --> 00:03:03,280
There are many parts in the factory. Dogs are not allowed.

48
00:03:03,280 --> 00:03:04,120
Follow me.

49
00:03:04,680 --> 00:03:05,200
Okay.

50
00:03:05,560 --> 00:03:07,080
Keke, come here.

51
00:03:07,960 --> 00:03:08,680
Keke.

52
00:03:08,880 --> 00:03:10,480
Be good. Don't run around.

53
00:03:14,000 --> 00:03:15,600
Tell me, what do you want?

54
00:03:18,280 --> 00:03:18,880
Sit.

55
00:03:19,600 --> 00:03:20,160
Sit down.

56
00:03:20,880 --> 00:03:22,640
Crazy dog, stay out of this.

57
00:03:25,040 --> 00:03:25,640
By the way.

58
00:03:37,040 --> 00:03:38,120
Don't tell me

59
00:03:39,000 --> 00:03:39,880
this is for me.

60
00:03:40,280 --> 00:03:41,000
Yes.

61
00:03:41,360 --> 00:03:43,760
This is what I poured out of the piggy bank

62
00:03:43,760 --> 00:03:44,840
I've been saving for a long time,

63
00:03:44,840 --> 00:03:46,079
along with what I found in the books,

64
00:03:46,079 --> 00:03:47,000
dug out from under the bed,

65
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:48,440
and turned out of my pockets.

66
00:03:48,440 --> 00:03:49,400
It's all here.

67
00:03:49,880 --> 00:03:51,800
A total of 498.5 yuan.

68
00:03:51,840 --> 00:03:52,520
Count it.

69
00:03:55,400 --> 00:03:57,000
I can't be bothered to count.

70
00:03:57,280 --> 00:03:59,079
No, you must count it carefully.

71
00:03:59,240 --> 00:04:01,040
Not a single cent can be missing.

72
00:04:05,560 --> 00:04:06,840
Could it really be her?

73
00:04:09,280 --> 00:04:10,880
What are you thinking about?

74
00:04:11,520 --> 00:04:12,200
Let me tell you.

75
00:04:12,200 --> 00:04:13,760
I recently got a big gig,

76
00:04:13,840 --> 00:04:15,240
walking dogs part-time.

77
00:04:15,240 --> 00:04:16,680
500 for three days.

78
00:04:16,959 --> 00:04:18,220
I can pay you back soon.

79
00:04:20,560 --> 00:04:21,279
Well,

80
00:04:21,560 --> 00:04:23,160
if there's nothing else,

81
00:04:23,320 --> 00:04:24,440
I'll take off now.

82
00:04:24,920 --> 00:04:25,200
Bye.

83
00:04:32,040 --> 00:04:32,900
Where is my dog?

84
00:04:33,640 --> 00:04:34,720
Zhu Keke.

85
00:04:35,520 --> 00:04:36,480
Dahuo.

86
00:04:38,320 --> 00:04:39,159
I'm doomed.

87
00:04:39,240 --> 00:04:41,120
This dog is worth more than my life.

88
00:04:41,120 --> 00:04:43,520
I could hear your voices from the backyard.

89
00:04:43,560 --> 00:04:44,600
What happened?

90
00:04:45,040 --> 00:04:46,880
Sir, I lost my dog here.

91
00:04:47,280 --> 00:04:49,340
If I can't find it, I'm really doomed.

92
00:04:49,400 --> 00:04:50,120
Tianyu.

93
00:04:51,080 --> 00:04:52,680
Hurry up and help her find it.

94
00:04:52,760 --> 00:04:54,890
Someone has to watch the factory, Dad.

95
00:04:55,080 --> 00:04:56,810
I'm here watching the factory.

96
00:04:56,880 --> 00:04:57,480
Go.

97
00:04:58,120 --> 00:04:59,080
Let's go. Hurry.

98
00:04:59,480 --> 00:05:00,680
Zhu Keke.

99
00:05:01,520 --> 00:05:02,800
Zhu Keke.

100
00:05:03,800 --> 00:05:05,200
Zhu Keke.

101
00:05:08,000 --> 00:05:09,000
Zhu Keke.

102
00:05:14,640 --> 00:05:15,840
Zhu Keke.

103
00:05:24,480 --> 00:05:25,400
It's so hot.

104
00:05:25,560 --> 00:05:27,220
Have an ice cream to cool down.

105
00:05:29,600 --> 00:05:31,120
Doudou can't eat ice cream.

106
00:05:31,120 --> 00:05:32,450
Otherwise, it will die.

107
00:05:39,040 --> 00:05:40,000
Eat it yourself.

108
00:05:40,200 --> 00:05:41,360
The thing I hate eating the most in my life

109
00:05:41,360 --> 00:05:42,360
is ice cream.

110
00:05:42,600 --> 00:05:44,280
Especially chocolate flavor.

111
00:05:44,280 --> 00:05:45,600
I already bought it. Just have one.

112
00:05:45,600 --> 00:05:47,200
You eat it. I won't.

113
00:05:48,280 --> 00:05:49,880
It seems it's really not her.

114
00:05:50,280 --> 00:05:53,680
Chocolate ice cream has been her favorite since she was a kid.

115
00:05:53,920 --> 00:05:54,560
Forget it.

116
00:05:56,800 --> 00:05:58,840
Dad, I want to ask you.

117
00:05:59,159 --> 00:06:00,760
In what way am I worse than Tianyu?

118
00:06:00,760 --> 00:06:02,840
He lost 2,000 yuan on one trip,

119
00:06:03,080 --> 00:06:04,200
and even had to pay out of pocket.

120
00:06:04,200 --> 00:06:05,960
Do you think everything he does is right?

121
00:06:05,960 --> 00:06:07,520
You are too biased.

122
00:06:07,800 --> 00:06:08,560
Yaqi,

123
00:06:09,920 --> 00:06:11,800
Tianyu has always been sensible.

124
00:06:12,800 --> 00:06:14,800
But you always try to drive him away.

125
00:06:15,360 --> 00:06:16,560
You are so impulsive.

126
00:06:16,800 --> 00:06:18,240
How can I trust you

127
00:06:18,400 --> 00:06:19,530
to run this factory?

128
00:06:20,080 --> 00:06:22,740
You should learn more skills from your brother.

129
00:06:22,880 --> 00:06:24,240
It will help you.

130
00:06:24,440 --> 00:06:26,440
Don't fool around all day.

131
00:06:26,600 --> 00:06:27,520
Learn skills?

132
00:06:28,720 --> 00:06:29,280
Okay.

133
00:06:29,480 --> 00:06:30,320
Back then,

134
00:06:30,800 --> 00:06:32,840
when you were the boss of the racing club,

135
00:06:32,840 --> 00:06:34,360
you only taught Tianyu how to race

136
00:06:34,360 --> 00:06:35,490
and made him a racer.

137
00:06:35,720 --> 00:06:37,320
When did you ever think of me?

138
00:06:37,800 --> 00:06:39,930
Now you think of me for repairing cars.

139
00:06:40,840 --> 00:06:43,280
I thought you were not suitable back then.

140
00:06:43,280 --> 00:06:44,080
Not suitable?

141
00:06:44,159 --> 00:06:46,420
So repairing cars is suitable for me now?

142
00:06:47,040 --> 00:06:49,240
Repairing cars doesn't suit me either.

143
00:06:49,320 --> 00:06:51,120
Whether I'm in this house or not,

144
00:06:51,920 --> 00:06:53,250
it makes no difference.

145
00:06:53,560 --> 00:06:54,240
Yaqi.

146
00:06:54,640 --> 00:06:55,280
Yaqi!

147
00:06:59,720 --> 00:07:01,160
Zhu Keke.

148
00:07:01,800 --> 00:07:03,000
Zhu Keke.

149
00:07:20,040 --> 00:07:21,200
What should we do?

150
00:07:22,400 --> 00:07:25,000
We've been looking for so long and still can't find him.

151
00:07:25,000 --> 00:07:27,000
Dahuo must be very scared right now.

152
00:07:27,160 --> 00:07:28,720
With just the two of us looking like this,

153
00:07:28,720 --> 00:07:30,180
when will we ever find him?

154
00:07:30,200 --> 00:07:31,520
Aren't you walking it for someone?

155
00:07:31,520 --> 00:07:33,040
Ask the dog's owner for help.

156
00:07:33,040 --> 00:07:35,100
If we can't find it, I guess the dog...

157
00:07:35,600 --> 00:07:36,680
Don't talk nonsense.

158
00:07:36,680 --> 00:07:37,920
If it's really gone,

159
00:07:38,120 --> 00:07:40,980
selling three of me wouldn't be enough to pay for it.

160
00:07:49,080 --> 00:07:51,280
Zhu Keke.

161
00:07:51,440 --> 00:07:53,900
Without you, how will your father Zhu Junchi

162
00:07:54,080 --> 00:07:56,440
ever survive?

163
00:07:58,560 --> 00:07:59,720
No, you can't die.

164
00:07:59,840 --> 00:08:01,560
Call the dog owner right away.

165
00:08:04,680 --> 00:08:05,680
Hello, cousin.

166
00:08:06,520 --> 00:08:07,280
Um,

167
00:08:08,240 --> 00:08:10,240
Dahuo is missing.

168
00:08:11,280 --> 00:08:12,000
What?

169
00:08:12,360 --> 00:08:13,000
Missing?

170
00:08:13,880 --> 00:08:14,720
I'm sorry.

171
00:08:15,080 --> 00:08:15,880
Su Wan,

172
00:08:16,160 --> 00:08:18,360
do you know how hard it is to raise my son?

173
00:08:18,840 --> 00:08:21,120
He is a purebred English Golden Retriever.

174
00:08:21,120 --> 00:08:23,680
with over 10 million fans across the internet.

175
00:08:23,680 --> 00:08:25,280
I know. I know. I know.

176
00:08:25,480 --> 00:08:26,280
Well, Cousin,

177
00:08:26,280 --> 00:08:27,740
can I just compensate you?

178
00:08:27,840 --> 00:08:28,900
Compensate my ass.

179
00:08:29,080 --> 00:08:30,320
Is this about money?

180
00:08:30,600 --> 00:08:31,080
Look,

181
00:08:31,160 --> 00:08:33,080
for the sake of us being cousins,

182
00:08:33,200 --> 00:08:34,360
please calm down, okay?

183
00:08:34,360 --> 00:08:36,159
Wan, I'm telling you.

184
00:08:36,320 --> 00:08:38,080
If my son is really lost,

185
00:08:38,919 --> 00:08:40,520
I will sacrifice you to heaven.

186
00:08:40,520 --> 00:08:42,179
You stay there and wait for me.

187
00:08:45,720 --> 00:08:46,280
Here.

188
00:08:46,440 --> 00:08:47,960
One hundred and fifty flyers.

189
00:08:47,960 --> 00:08:48,560
Right now,

190
00:08:49,400 --> 00:08:50,680
cover every street with them.

191
00:08:50,680 --> 00:08:52,240
If we can't find him tonight,

192
00:08:52,240 --> 00:08:53,120
you're dead.

193
00:08:57,360 --> 00:08:57,680
Who are you?

194
00:08:57,680 --> 00:08:58,160
Who are you?

195
00:08:58,160 --> 00:08:58,960
Her creditor.

196
00:09:02,800 --> 00:09:03,840
30,000.

197
00:09:06,760 --> 00:09:08,690
Humans really are worse than dogs.

198
00:09:08,960 --> 00:09:10,080
If I find him,

199
00:09:10,200 --> 00:09:12,640
I don't want 30,000, just 3,000.

200
00:09:12,760 --> 00:09:14,290
Can you help me pay him back?

201
00:09:14,480 --> 00:09:16,560
Su Wan, what are you thinking?

202
00:09:16,680 --> 00:09:18,040
The only reason I haven't killed you yet

203
00:09:18,040 --> 00:09:19,840
is because I need an extra hand to find my son.

204
00:09:19,840 --> 00:09:21,300
How dare you ask for money?

205
00:09:21,480 --> 00:09:23,600
Brother, can we talk about this?

206
00:09:24,000 --> 00:09:24,520
Su Wan.

207
00:09:24,720 --> 00:09:26,560
I'm giving you 24 hours

208
00:09:26,680 --> 00:09:27,720
to find my son.

209
00:09:35,040 --> 00:09:36,040
Zhu Keke.

210
00:09:42,800 --> 00:09:43,480
Guys,

211
00:09:44,120 --> 00:09:45,680
my son's social media account,

212
00:09:45,680 --> 00:09:46,810
'Zhu Keke's Daily',

213
00:09:47,000 --> 00:09:48,930
might pause updates for a few days.

214
00:09:53,000 --> 00:09:54,040
As you all know,

215
00:09:54,640 --> 00:09:56,800
my son is a purebred English Golden Retriever.

216
00:09:56,800 --> 00:09:58,720
If anyone has clues, please DM me.

217
00:09:59,240 --> 00:10:01,480
I'm willing to pay a 30,000 reward.

218
00:10:02,440 --> 00:10:03,040
Please.

219
00:10:13,160 --> 00:10:15,690
It's not too much to teach you a lesson, right?

220
00:10:16,520 --> 00:10:19,780
You're the one who caused the factory to lose so much money.

221
00:10:20,120 --> 00:10:20,880
30,000.

222
00:10:21,480 --> 00:10:23,010
This dog is quite valuable.

223
00:10:38,240 --> 00:10:39,560
Hello, Cousin.

224
00:10:40,000 --> 00:10:41,600
Someone shared a clue with me.

225
00:10:41,600 --> 00:10:42,320
Go there quickly.

226
00:10:42,320 --> 00:10:43,650
Help me see if it's Keke.

227
00:10:43,800 --> 00:10:44,860
I'm on my way there.

228
00:10:44,920 --> 00:10:46,400
Okay, I'll go right now.

229
00:10:48,440 --> 00:10:49,840
Where is this?

230
00:10:56,960 --> 00:10:59,080
Isn't this the next street?

231
00:10:59,280 --> 00:11:00,440
The next street?

232
00:11:01,360 --> 00:11:02,620
Then let's hurry over.

233
00:11:10,400 --> 00:11:11,800
Is this the place?

234
00:11:15,080 --> 00:11:17,120
Oh no, my phone is dead.

235
00:11:18,160 --> 00:11:19,640
Was the location sent wrong?

236
00:11:19,640 --> 00:11:20,400
Are you sure?

237
00:11:20,520 --> 00:11:22,560
Whether it is or not, we should go in and look.

238
00:11:22,560 --> 00:11:24,280
What if Dahuo is really inside?

239
00:11:24,280 --> 00:11:24,810
Let's go.

240
00:11:41,000 --> 00:11:42,160
Zhu Keke.

241
00:11:43,840 --> 00:11:44,920
Zhu Keke.

242
00:11:46,480 --> 00:11:47,410
Where did she go?

243
00:11:47,680 --> 00:11:48,720
Zhu Keke.

244
00:11:50,560 --> 00:11:51,560
Could it be here?

245
00:11:51,760 --> 00:11:53,000
Did she send the wrong location?

246
00:11:53,000 --> 00:11:54,460
Let's go in and take a look.

247
00:11:55,600 --> 00:11:56,840
Zhu Keke.

248
00:11:57,600 --> 00:11:58,640
Zhu Keke.
